18
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:48,880
Seriously.

19
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,680
He's still a kid.

20
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:51,759
How rude.

21
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,160
Go find a doctor.

22
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:55,440
Don't let him get sick.

23
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:56,560
Wait a minute.

24
00:01:57,640 --> 00:02:00,360
Prepare something delicious

25
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:01,440
Four dishes and one soup.

26
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:02,320
Half meat and half vegetables.

27
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:04,240
Brother, if we do this,

28
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:05,200
if we do this,

29
00:02:05,440 --> 00:02:07,320
It's okay. I'll take care of it. Go ahead.

30
00:02:11,039 --> 00:02:12,240
Wake up.

31
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:14,000
Sir! Sir!

32
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:14,880
Bad news!

33
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:17,120
Poppet was captured by the bandits of Qingfeng Camp.

34
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:18,360
