35
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,640
You're dead if you don't pay.

36
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:20,760
Shan Shan.

37
00:02:20,760 --> 00:02:23,120
500 taels.

38
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:26,040
Why didn't they rob it?

39
00:02:26,079 --> 00:02:26,840
They did.

40
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:28,040
Didn't they fail?

41
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:29,680
What about Poppet's family?

42
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:31,200
Even if they sell the house,

43
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:32,440
even if they sell the house.

44
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:34,480
Wait.

45
00:02:34,480 --> 00:02:35,920
Let me think of a way.

46
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:39,720
This...

47
00:02:39,720 --> 00:02:40,320
What should we do?

48
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,000
This...

49
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:42,280
Let's go. Let's go.

50
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:43,160
Don't.

51
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:44,520
Let alone Her Ladyship,

52
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:46,560
