66
00:03:18,920 --> 00:03:22,000
But I'm also the magistrate.

67
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:24,840
I'm a parent in Gusu County.

68
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:27,320
Isn't it my duty to save people?

69
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:28,520
What do you think, madam?

70
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:30,280
Responsibility?

71
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:33,120
