79
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:04,080
I don't want anything to happen to the baby.

80
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:07,840
We can only think of other ways.

81
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:13,200
I know you love me the most.

82
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:17,519
Please don't be angry.

83
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:18,279
Calm down.

84
00:04:19,959 --> 00:04:21,560
Sir, are you looking for me?

85
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:27,840
Did you deliver the ransom?

86
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:31,000
Probably on the way.

87
00:04:31,320 --> 00:04:32,320
Don't worry.

88
00:04:34,520 --> 00:04:35,440
No hurry.

89
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:40,120
Cut his ear and send it to them.

90
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,360
Brother.

91
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:42,800
Alright.

92
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:21,440
500 taels of silver.

93
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:24,200
Xu Sanniang.

94
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,320
Thank you.

95
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,680
Don't fight. It's me.

96
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:48,040
Li Renyi, the second head of Qingfeng Camp.

97
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,880
I'm here to send you the child.

98
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:56,760
Be gentle, kid.

99
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,520
I'll give you 500 taels of ransom.

100
