116
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:54,040
Thank you so much.

117
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:55,840
It's nothing.

118
00:06:55,840 --> 00:06:56,640
Thank you.

119
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:59,080
My lady

120
