123
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,000
No.

124
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:10,400
He didn't say anything

125
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:11,880
didn't say anything.

126
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:14,040
